document_data.caption: A map showing Callidyrr Ride in Aithelar.
document_data.name: Callidyrr Ride
document_data.mainbody: '''Callidyrr Ride''' was a street found in the coastal town of [[Aithelar]] in [[Callidyrr]] on the [[Moonshae Isles]] in {{YearlinkName|1345}}.{{Cite interactive atlas}}
document_data.Location: Callidyrr Ride was found in southwest Aithelar in between [[Finn's Alley]] and [[Blackdorn's Way]]. [[Aerynn's Street]] branched from its midpoint to the northeast.
